  "vulnerability_information": "Apache Airflow, versions 2.10.5, is affected by a vulnerability that allows an attacker can manipulate query construction, leading to an SQL Injection vulnerability that may result in remote code execution.\n\n## Impact\n\nThe DAGS that use the SQLColumnCheckOperator in the system will remote code execution.",
